/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/squid-game-the-challenge"><em>鱿鱼游戏：挑战赛</em></a>选手065在被观众贴上“恶棍”和“垃圾”标签后，为自己在弹珠游戏中的行为进行了辩护。</p><ul><li data-cy="Paragraph" data-experiment="{&quot;widget&quot;:true}"><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/will-there-be-squid-game-the-challenge-season-two-3550855">会有“鱿鱼游戏：挑战”第二季吗？</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>的新游戏节目改编<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/squid-game">自热门韩剧，</a>现实生活中的参赛者将在一系列儿童游戏中展开角逐，争夺 456 万美元的现金奖励。</p><p>然而，有些参赛者诚实地玩游戏，而另一些参赛者则采用肮脏的策略——就像韩剧本身一样——玩家被观众贴上英雄或恶棍的标签。</p><p>迪伦，又名玩家 065，由于他在第六集中与玩家 399（奥罗拉）进行弹珠游戏比赛时的可疑行为而属于后一类。</p><p>该游戏要求两人在 20 分钟内设计并玩弹珠游戏，失败者将被淘汰。然而，如果一对选手在时间限制结束时未能选出获胜者，则两名选手都将被淘汰。 </p><figure id="attachment_3546448" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3546448" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3546448" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1.jpg" alt="鱿鱼游戏：挑战" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3546448" class="wp-caption-text"> 《鱿鱼游戏：挑战》第一集。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p> 《玩家065》和《玩家399》就是如此。迪伦因拒绝向奥罗拉妥协而受到观众批评，奥罗拉想要玩一个不涉及投掷的游戏。迪伦还指责他的伴侣“提高了声音”，尽管事实上她没有。</p><p>最终，奥罗拉同意玩投掷游戏。但尽管她是第一个将弹子放入彩池的人，迪伦还是拒绝让她获胜，两名选手都被淘汰了。</p><p>一位观众对迪伦的行为感到愤怒，称他是<em>《鱿鱼游戏：挑战》</em>中的“真正的恶棍”。另一个人说：“我不喜欢他对她提高声音的评论，因为她似乎在用平静、正常的语气说话。这感觉就像是一种微侵略，”第三个人回答道：“哦，是的。我确实看到了。这给人的印象是很糟糕。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C0QYde8uVZj/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 53